# JOKE YA MIND ENGINE – PART 23: WRAITH WORLD VOTE & SAVE SLOTS
# =============================================================================
# This code appends after Part 22, adding:
# - Hidden Wraith World Vote system (based on boredom, curiosity, aspiration)
# - Vote triggers world reset or major event before save wipe/new game
# - 3 default save slots with slider for additional slots (configurable)
# - Start menu displays slots with name, timestamp, preview
# - Save/load system extended to handle multiple slots
# - Integration with pause menu and new game flow
